General.Name: Munsin Garment
General.Description: Munsin Garment Corporation manufactures and trades in various knitwear garments in Taiwan. The company offers golf apparel, lightweight sportswear, professional bicycles, equestrian sports products, casual wear, cue bags, handbags, protective accessories, special clothing, sneakers, shirts, trousers, and sporting products, as well as jogging, tennis, and football series products. It is also involved in the product distribution, import, and export businesses. Munsin Garment Corporation provides its products under the Munsingwear, Le coq sportif, Felix Buhler, McGREGOR, HAZZYS, ACUPUNCTURE, NARA CAMICIE, Eminento, As know as de base, POU DOU DOU, and Danskin brands. Munsin Garment Corporation was founded in 1966 and is headquartered in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
General.Address: No. 18, Wuquan 6th Road, New Taipei City, Taiwan
